rfassers? Wer erzählt und wer signiert die Autobiography of Alice B. Toklas? Kann Hannah Arendt in der Lebensgeschichte einer deutschen Jüdin aus der Romantik die Autobiographie Rahel Varnhagens schreiben?  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 01. Dez 2022) 4aAllgemeine Literaturwissenschaft. 4aAmerikanistik. 4aAutobiographie. 4aGender Studies. 4aGender. 4aGermanistik. 4aLiteratur. 4aLiteraturtheorie. 4aLiteraturwissenschaft. 4aUrheberrecht. 7aLITERARY CRITICISM / Semiotics & Theory.2bisacsh  aAmerican Studies.  aGender.  aGeneral Literature Studies.  aGerman Literature.  aLiterary Studies.  aLiterature.  aTheory of Literature.08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe Gruyterttranscript Backlist eBook Package 2000-2013z978311102523008iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe Gruyterttranscript Highlight Collection Complete Package 2000-2009z9783110463415oZDB-23-TSO08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe Gruyterttranscript Highlight Collection Lit. & Kultur 2000-2009z97831104634080 cprintz978389942375440uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/9783839403754?locatt=mode:legacy40uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783839403754423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9783839403754/original  a978-3-11-046340-8  transcript Highlight Collection Lit. & Kultur 2000-2009c2000d2009  a978-3-11-102523-0  transcript Backlist eBook Package 2000-2013c2000d2013  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_CL_LS  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_PPALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA5EBK  aZDB-23-TSOc2000d2009